#steam
######

With Gecko gone MIA I was unable to obtain official permission. I intend to release the mod back to him should he resurface. If simply editting his work turns out to be problematic I will do a full rewrite instead.

Only changes made so far were to remove a lot of redundency and update to include melee weapons. Weapon Box craftable from second tier inventors table.

Explicitly compatible with [url=http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=836238594]Grand Armory[/url]!

